Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.75,0:00:19.53,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士星矢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.32,0:00:25.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在没有星光的迷宫里挣扎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:30.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彷徨的少年啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.95,0:00:36.10,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感受灵魂的呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:41.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙正在呼唤你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.30,0:00:47.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,背负伤痕 知晓孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.65,0:00:52.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于明白了羁绊的意义
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:55.36,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消除阴翳眼眸中的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.60,0:00:57.99,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安和困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.30,0:01:04.50,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃烧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.87,0:01:08.33,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士们 站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.50,0:01:11.00,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,迎向未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.20,0:01:14.42,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果背负的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:16.35,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够称为爱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.43,0:01:19.05,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战士们相互支持
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:21.68,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化为风的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:26.15,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全新的Ω神话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.27,0:01:31.40,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就从现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.60,0:00:21.00,LOGO,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光荣字幕组&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.16,0:01:44.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好壮观！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.76,0:01:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里就是五老峰吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.37,0:01:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好让人兴奋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.98,0:01:53.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们再慢慢吞吞的我就丢下你们了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.26,0:01:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这种程度 也能算青铜圣斗士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.45,0:01:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:01:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是叫昴来着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 很嚣张地说“我要打倒你成为神”的钢铁圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.06,0:02:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 别看他那个样子 关键时候还是很能干的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.71,0:02:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒觉得他只是个自大的小鬼而已
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.94,0:02:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 昴
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.60,0:02:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么那么干劲十足啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.41,0:02:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在要去找的那个叫龙峰的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.00,0:02:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个传说中的圣斗士 天龙座紫龙的儿子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.10,0:02:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.21,0:02:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是我们之中 比任何人都更具才能的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.59,0:02:30.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.72,0:02:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要打倒他 变得更强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.45,0:02:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？喂！别想那些傻事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.86,0:02:52.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自银河飞流而下的庐山大瀑布
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将其水流 逆流回天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.30,0:03:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无可替代之物！觉醒吧、龙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.77,0:03:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 这对我太困难了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.36,0:03:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我不穿圣衣 就将这庐山大瀑布逆流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.56,0:03:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰 别泄气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.97,0:03:34.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有如攀升银河的龙一般 将这大瀑布逆流回天
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.97,0:03:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是真正的天龙座圣斗士的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗明明已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.98,0:03:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣斗士的战斗永无止境
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.36,0:03:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了地上的爱与和平而战斗的希望的斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前往嘉米尔并且修复了圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.31,0:04:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你却无法穿上圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:05.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为你的内心尚有迷惘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.92,0:04:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提升小宇宙 超越自己的极限之时
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就可以再次穿上圣衣了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.18,0:04:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这话我已经听腻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.98,0:04:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的体内也有龙在沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以力量改变逆境 不断攀登高峰的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:30.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒那条龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.88,0:04:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿嘿 快点来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.93,0:04:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是女神帕拉斯大人的仆从
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:51.69,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.16,0:04:51.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奉三级刻斗士 哈利墨德大人之命而来  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.82,0:04:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.18,0:04:55.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此路不通！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.82,0:04:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看来你们的目标是龙峰吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.18,0:04:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 战斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.08,0:05:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 天马座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.84,0:05:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼狮座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天鹰座
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.02,0:05:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也上了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.10,0:05:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 钢铁圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.32,0:06:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.92,0:06:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事 给我滚开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么打下去没完没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.71,0:06:39.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.07,0:06:49.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.75,0:06:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰 你终于平安归来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.63,0:06:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰 我感觉到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.37,0:07:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那在同黑暗之神阿普斯的战斗中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.52,0:07:12.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精进磨砺 愈发强大的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.04,0:07:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经成长为一名出色的圣斗士了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.14,0:07:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是依靠父亲的教诲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.96,0:07:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才能通过一场又一场战斗的考验
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.31,0:07:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我的战斗已经结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.52,0:07:29.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这天龙座圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也应该回到它原来的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.46,0:07:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲您的手中了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:37.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这圣衣是属于你的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.86,0:07:40.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要它的时刻也将再次到来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论发生什么 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不能让它离开你的身边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.14,0:07:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 圣衣已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.35,0:07:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可知这圣衣的由来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.93,0:07:57.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天龙座圣衣在这大瀑布的最深处
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.64,0:07:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在堪称永恒的漫长时间里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.52,0:08:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,历经银河之水的击打锤炼 最终孕育而生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并因此具备了凌驾于钻石之上的光芒与硬度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你不将圣衣披挂于身
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.11,0:08:12.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它将再次在大瀑布深处
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.68,0:08:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷入长久的沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 只要你不断提升自己的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.09,0:08:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣衣也定会回应你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.39,0:08:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.34,0:08:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:40.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本以为 回到五老峰就能与父亲母亲 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家三口过上幸福的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是父亲他却…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲您又是怎么想的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.71,0:08:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.93,0:08:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我出生之前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.59,0:08:53.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲就以圣斗士的身份不断战斗着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:57.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛下母亲 冒着生命危险投身战场
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.72,0:08:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且身受重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.00,0:09:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面对这一切 您真的能够坦然以对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.30,0:09:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这就是 圣斗士的宿命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:10.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲他拥有许多伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.24,0:09:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了同伴 他不惜身负重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.43,0:09:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奋不顾身地投入战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天龙座圣衣 可是你父亲与同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上性命并肩作战的证明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.80,0:09:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰 你也曾与无可取代的同伴们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.94,0:09:29.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并肩战斗过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.05,0:09:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:09:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.18,0:10:00.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少 让我稍事休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.93,0:10:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 敌人可不会等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.80,0:10:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.64,0:10:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗之神阿普斯已经消亡了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.11,0:10:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人已经不存在了不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.31,0:10:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管再怎么修炼 也没有任何意义啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.08,0:10:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 您听我说
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.73,0:10:22.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我与同伴们战斗至今的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.83,0:10:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了父亲您
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.79,0:10:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直认为 只要我能够提升自己的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.42,0:10:30.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就可以使五感尽失的父亲您恢复原状
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.45,0:10:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我所期待的生活并不是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不想再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.94,0:10:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想和父亲母亲一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:42.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一家三口过上平静的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.39,0:10:50.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃它 也就意味着抛弃与同伴之间的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.76,0:10:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:12.41,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉醒吧！龙之圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.92,0:11:28.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抛弃它 也就意味着抛弃与同伴之间的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.80,0:11:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你无所谓吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.83,0:11:37.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 就因为被无谓的家族之情所绊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.12,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你才一直这么弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.96,0:11:45.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女神帕拉斯大人的仆从　三级刻斗士哈利墨德
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.93,0:11:49.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有我这三节棍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻斗士？！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒黑暗之神阿普斯的圣斗士…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的性命 我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.31,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道父亲提到的敌人就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解决掉你之后就轮到紫龙了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.77,0:12:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你休想动我父亲一根指头
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:09.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 逞强就只有现在了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.34,0:12:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就让你这软骨头见识一下 什么是真正的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.41,0:12:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有圣衣的圣斗士 完全不够看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.42,0:12:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 真无聊 给你个痛快的算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 别过来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰 你父亲让你拿上这个
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.66,0:13:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.37,0:13:08.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣衣吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会让你穿上它的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.49,0:13:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真傻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.28,0:13:18.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲早就预见新的敌人正在逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才硬下心 让我进行严酷的试炼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.05,0:13:25.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我却什么都不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:27.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.93,0:13:32.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 真碍眼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.84,0:13:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.91,0:13:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是早就说过 你太过天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.61,0:13:52.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然为家人牺牲自己
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想像大爷我一样变得强大
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.32,0:13:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就给我彻底丢掉那种玩意儿 专心战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样就能变强了 就像大爷我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.17,0:14:09.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我能变强 正是因为有父亲母亲在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.21,0:14:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能一路战胜困难走到今天
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.90,0:14:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早说过你那想法太过幼稚了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 这种东西 看我废了它
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:30.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:34.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这小子真难缠
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.68,0:14:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你刚才不是自己舍弃那圣衣的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:39.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老老实实放弃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.23,0:14:41.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.88,0:14:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是父亲传给我的重要的圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.68,0:14:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我与同伴曾经并肩战斗的证明
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.32,0:14:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死也不会交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.66,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 那就去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣衣啊 再次赐予我力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.07,0:15:14.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要守护无可替代的家人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.13,0:15:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守护父亲和母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.20,0:15:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此 不惜舍弃生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的体内也有龙在沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.94,0:15:33.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以力量改变逆境 不断攀登高峰的龙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.59,0:15:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唤醒那条龙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:45.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使头破血流 即使身体四分五裂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也要为重要的人赌上生命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.72,0:15:51.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是真正的圣斗士
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了守护父亲母亲 我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.02,0:16:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奔涌吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.79,0:16:28.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…天龙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.15,0:16:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.31,0:16:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 天龙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.70,0:17:12.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是…我的新生圣衣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:19.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 不过是穿上了圣衣 有什么好神气的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.62,0:17:38.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是新生圣衣 防御能力明显提升了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.91,0:17:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光耀射击（Flare Shoot）！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.05,0:17:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.05,0:18:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全身涌起力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.39,0:18:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圣衣…正回应着我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:13.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喷涌吧 我的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.14,0:18:21.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庐山升龙霸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.53,0:18:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我记住
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次我一定会干掉你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:05.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉睡的龙好像觉醒了啊 龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 您看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在注视着你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.39,0:19:12.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.41,0:19:15.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的话 即使没有我的帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.92,0:19:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定能奋战到底
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.37,0:19:20.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰！没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:28.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻斗士盯上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.10,0:19:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.05,0:19:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不要大意了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.90,0:19:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.19,0:19:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人没有来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.45,0:19:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道说…已经打倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.21,0:19:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.04,0:20:12.58,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一级刻斗士 泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.25,0:20:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.39,0:20:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我名为泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.07,0:20:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是侍奉您 守护您之人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.14,0:20:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后 您无论有何事 都请吩咐我泰坦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.84,0:20:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 请多指教哦 泰坦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.16,0:20:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲 母亲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.10,0:21:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从今往后也会继续战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:05.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到迎来三人一起平静生活的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.53,0:21:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好表现哦 龙峰
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信同伴吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:12.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 前进之路自然会敞开
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.07,0:21:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 天龙座紫龙的儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我决一胜负吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.15,0:21:23.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…你还没做过自我介绍呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.85,0:21:25.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小朋友 你的名字是？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.45,0:21:26.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别叫我小朋友！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.76,0:21:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫昴
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.15,0:21:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家 我接下来打算去找荣斗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家回到圣域 跟其他的圣斗士汇合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.54,0:21:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要小心 光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.21,0:21:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 荣斗我记得是…天狼座？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.49,0:21:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 那家伙现在好像在故乡日本
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:21:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.55,0:22:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想见见荣斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.68,0:22:29.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天狼之声在都市中回响
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.60,0:22:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开黑暗追寻光明的忍者
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.42,0:22:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回到披挂圣衣战斗的道路上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.39,0:22:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是握住话筒 铭刻心灵的呼喊呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.50,0:22:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,荣斗 追寻梦之狼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.34,0:22:45.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赌上人生 向着月亮嗥叫吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.93,0:22:47.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 圣斗士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响彻心灵！荣斗的嘶吼！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.69,0:22:53.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在吗